        <guid>https://solal2600.github.io/frprep/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://solal2600.github.io/category_france.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 法国留学-行前准备篇" /&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;行李清单&#34;&gt;行李清单&lt;/h2&gt;
